  "description": "The opening number. Medium 12-second S-curve arc that builds from near-silence to a rich, warm peak at 0.75. Vowel morphs from E to A — closed anticipation opening into full expression. 2-voice unison with gentle detune creates orchestral width. The arc that says: the show is about to begin.",
